what is class ?
class ak blueprint hoti or template bhe kha ja tha hai is may hum method or properties ko define kartay hai.
or isko blueprint isleya kha ja tha hain Q kay Ap Ak building banaa rahy ho tw us may Deisgn Banana thay Ho.
or Structure Banana thay Ho..
Tw Aesi he Hum Koo programming May Attitbuties Bananay Hotay ha Or Method define karnay Hotay ...

How Many type Of Access Modifer ;

Three type Of Access Modifer..
1)Public.
2)Protected.
3)Private.

Public :
        Ka matlab hota ha Kay Ap is koo kahe pay Access kar sakhu matlab ap nay ak function banaya employee_details ka ..
        tw ab us koo class may Access kar sakthy ho ya class Kay bahar bhe Access kar sakthy ha ho.

Protected :
            Protected ka matlab hota ha kay hum us class may he Access kar sakhtay jis class may ho or class kay bahre Access nhi kar sakhtay .
            lakin Hum isko Extend kar kay bhe Access kar sakthy hai..

Private :
          Private ka matlab ya hota ha kay hum us koo class may he Access kar sakhtay na class kay bahar na class Extend kara kay ..

How Many Pilars In Oop?

Is kay Four Pilars Hain.
1)Encapsulation
2)Inheritance
3)Polymorphisum  
4)Abstraction  

Encapsulation :
                Encapsulation ka matlab hai data aur methods ko ek unit (class) ke andar band karna. Isse data ki security badhti hai
                Aur unnecessary access se bachaya jata hai...

Inheritance :
             Inheritance mean ak class koo dousri class say Inheritance karna matlab presnet class or child class....


Polymorphisum :
            Polymorphism ka matlab hai ek method ko alag-alag classes me alag-alag tareeke se implement karna. 
            Ye overloading aur overriding ke zariye achieve hota hai.
            Isse ek hi function ya method ko alag objects ke liye different tareeke se behave karne diya jata hai.
            
            